{"tid":1086851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推到上報,香港成功回歸又一例證,厚顏抄襲","createTime":"2019-04-01T04:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T01:17:14.000Z","uid":196751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9f3ac0462cd2b14c883996b894224f7fb12764","tid":1086851,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:29:28.000Z","msg":"我自己幾鍾意食野,全香港周圍食<br />\n其實細心睇下會發覺香港好多鋪頭都係鍾意抄<br />\n今日同大家介紹兩間特別抄得勁,係連裝修餐牌都抄到一樣既餐廳<br />\n<br />\n原店:老鳳冰室: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0mjC600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0mjC600&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=e9113b35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0mjC600</a><br />\n抄襲:<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0bMy3W0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0bMy3W0&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=57fba8e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0bMy3W0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原店:蘇媽.蘇媽<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Taa800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0Taa800&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=b903cb9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Taa800</a><br />\n抄襲:<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0up4900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0up4900&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=2ea5a197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0up4900</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Gz2400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0Gz2400&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=a2290dbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Gz2400</a><br />\n(店員話同一老細)<br />\n<br />\n由其係馬拉菜蘇媽係幾好食,所以佢由小店果陣我就幫襯<br />\n果陣無裝修,係冷巷開<br />\n到依加開左鋪,靚左,出左名就走兩間自稱佢地先係正宗既老翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正宗點解要裝修餐牌都抄埋人?<br />\n<br />\n香港仲有好多抄襲餐廳,呢兩個例子係我所知最無恥既一檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf2995ca510af200bd5049df4ed5b3ca4fa652d","tid":1086851,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d9f7d50ef7ff38454df8dad660260bc9e7a20c","tid":1086851,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2df8e7810b6e82802dacc7b221e085af54d1bd","tid":1086851,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"香港人唔配講知識版權?"},{"pid":"62a1a4d35d90d65d2d1e0b8b9a1fb39618eb0560","tid":1086851,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0600626f15e964e854b1bc1a4f99c2916f51a1a6","tid":1086851,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffebc5443f82573ca9d6ca2d613c5bd9d838cb0","tid":1086851,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af1e7247c64e96acdd30348809b055df75a587a","tid":1086851,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}